_2024</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hustdmin.github.io/blog/2024/MICCAI_2024/"><![CDATA[<p>2024年10月6日至2024年10月10日，喻莉教授、闫增强副教授、林娴博士受邀参加第27届国际医学图像计算和计算机辅助干预会议（MICCAI 2024），该会议是医学图像分析领域国际公认的最具影响力的学术会议，聚焦医学影像计算和计算机辅助干预领域的最新研究和技术创新。MICCAI 2024于摩洛哥马拉喀什举办，大会共收稿2879篇，最终录取857篇，DMIN实验室投稿的4篇论文均被接收。</p> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 480px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI1-480.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 800px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI1-800.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 1400px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI1-1400.webp"/> <img src="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI1.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="auto" height="auto" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> </div> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 480px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI2-480.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 800px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI2-800.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 1400px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI2-1400.webp"/> <img src="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI2.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="auto" height="auto" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> </div> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 480px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI3-480.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 800px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI3-800.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 1400px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-MICCAI3-1400.webp"/> <